title: Sausage Maple Biscuit
description: Our baked in house, warm, fluffy Maple Biscuit topped with a sausage patty.

title: Maple Bacon Super Biscuit
description: Our Made from Scratch™ Biscuit topped with cherrywood-smoked bacon prepared in house, with caramelized maple, sugar, and spices then topped with American cheese and a freshly cracked fried egg. Due to the ongoing national egg shortage, eggs may be served folded rather than fried.

title: Biscuit 'N' Gravy
description: Get your goodness on with one of our warm, fluffy, freshly baked Made from Scratch™ Biscuits smothered in sausage gravy.

title: Frisco Breakfast Sandwich Combo
description: Rise n’ shine with this sandwich featuring thinly sliced ham, hearty egg, American & Swiss cheese all stacked on perfectly toasted sourdough. Hash Rounds® and your choice of beverage complete the perfect start to your day.

title: Maple Biscuit
description: Baked in house, warm, fluffy biscuit loaded with maple flavor and drizzled with icing. Available all day!

title: Maple Bacon Snack Pack
description: Cherrywood-smoked bacon prepared in house with caramelized maple, sugar, and spices, loaded into a portable pack for on-the-go snacking.

title: Maple Bacon Frisco Burger Combo
description: Our 100% Angus beef patty charbroiled over an open flame, then topped with four strips of crispy maple bacon, Swiss cheese tomatoes and mayonnaise, served on sourdough. A side of fries and your choice of drink complete the combo.

title: Nashville Hot Hand-Breaded Chicken Sandwich Combo
description: Enjoy chicken with a kick when you order this sandwich. Our premium, all white meat chicken fillet is dipped in buttermilk, lightly breaded and then fried to a golden brown before being topped with Nashville Hot seasoning. We then add a layer of pickles and serve it all on a perfectly toasted bun. We complete the combo with a beverage and side of fries.

title: Famous Star Combo
description: Good bites are waiting for those who order the Famous Star® Combo, featuring a Quarter Pound 100% Angus beef patty topped with melted American cheese, lettuce, tomatoes, sliced onions, dill pickles, Special Sauce, and mayonnaise - all on a perfectly toasted potato bun. Fries and a beverage complete the meal.
